The '''Soammei clan''' was a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clan from the [[Species/Legends|species]]' [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. Its homeland was west of the [[Chattza Bay]] on the [[Encheeko/Legends|Encheeko]] continent of the [[planet/Legends|planet]].

Through its domination of all other Rodians, the Soammei clan was the first to institute the title of "Inta'si'rin'na," or [[Grand Protector/Legends|Grand Protector of the Rodians]]. However, during the course of the following [[Standard century/Legends|centuries]] the clan was challenged and defended its leadership claim, until eventually it met its destruction at the hands of its enemies.

